All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ChatManager
The ChatManager class manages chat messages for the Yolo plugin.
ChatManager.ChatMessageType
This enum represents the different types of chat messages that can be sent by the Yolo plugin.
CommandRegistrar
This class is responsible for registering all commands of the plugin.
ReloadCommand
This is the CommandExecutor for the command yolo-reload.
ResourcePackManager
This is a utility class, that manages setting up a resource pack, as it is described in the plugin's config.
ReviveCommand
Currently not implemented, but is intended to revive a player upon the command revive [player] being called.
SpicordManager
This singleton is instantiated, when Spicord is also loaded as a Plugin.
SpicordManager.DiscordMessageType
Provides the types of messages, which can be sent to Discord.
TextReplacements
The TextReplacements enum provides a set of named text replacements that can be used to generate dynamic text in a message.
Yolo
A Bukkit plugin that adds features related to player deaths and Discord integration.
YoloEventListener
The event listener for this plugin.
YoloPluginCommandSender
This class is a custom CommandSender, that triggers commands on behalf of this plugin.
